<div class="row">
  <div class="col-md-12">
    <h2>Welcome, <%= user.username %></h2>
    <p>This is your decision matrix dashboard. Here you can manage your saved decisions and create new ones.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="row mt-4">
  <div class="col-md-6">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-header bg-primary text-white">
        <h3 class="mb-0">Quick Actions</h3>
      </div>
      <div class="card-body">
        <div class="d-grid gap-3">
          <a href="/" class="btn btn-primary">Create New Decision</a>
          <a href="/my-decisions" class="btn btn-outline-primary">View My Decisions</a>
          <a href="/logout" class="btn btn-outline-danger">Logout</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="col-md-6">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-header bg-primary text-white">
        <h3 class="mb-0">Account Information</h3>
      </div>
      <div class="card-body">
        <p><strong>Username:</strong> <%= user.username %></p>
        <p><strong>Email:</strong> <%= user.email %></p>
        <p><strong>Member Since:</strong> <%= new Date(user.createdAt).toLocaleDateString() %></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="row mt-4">
  <div class="col-md-12">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-header bg-primary text-white">
        <h3 class="mb-0">About Decision Matrix</h3>
      </div>
      <div class="card-body">
        <p>A decision matrix is a tool that helps you evaluate and prioritize options based on weighted criteria.</p>
        <p>How it works:</p>
        <ol>
          <li>Define your decision and criteria</li>
          <li>Assign weights to each criterion</li>
          <li>List your alternatives</li>
          <li>Evaluate each alternative against each criterion</li>
          <li>Calculate the results</li>
        </ol>
        <p>This app guides you through each step and saves your decisions for future reference.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div> 